
================================================================================
  PHASE 2 EXPANSION: ALL MISSING SCREEN SPECIFICATIONS
================================================================================
  Covers: B2, B3, B4, D2, D4, D5, D6, E1, E3, E4, F1, F2, G1,
          H1, H2, H3, H4, I1 + NLP Parser + Content Strategy + Design System
