  DSA / ALGORITHMS:
    - Grouping: multi-key sort (is_favorite DESC, lastModified DESC)
    - Search: trigram matching on project name (pg_trgm on backend, local prefix match)
    - Pagination: cursor-based for large project lists

  TESTS (target count):
